@startuml sd_SalaryItemService_create
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title SalaryItemService.create(item) - 创建工资项目

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryItemController" as Ctrl
participant "SalaryItemService" as Service
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as Repo

Client -> Ctrl: POST /api/salary-items\n{name, code, itemType, formula, sortOrder}
Ctrl -> Service: create(item)
Service -> Repo: save(item)
Repo --> Service: 持久化后SalaryItem
Service --> Ctrl: SalaryItem
note right of Service : @Transactional\n内置项标志builtIn=false\nactive默认true
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<SalaryItem>
@enduml
